Class VHMLOutputAccess

  metaface.client.VHMLOutputAccess

PrivilegedAction
class VHMLOutputAccess
extends Object
implements PrivilegedAction

This class allows XML parsing errors to propogate due to privileged actions. Otherwise a security exception will be thrown for XML errors.
